    "course_title": "LIFESPAN MOTOR DEVELOPMENT",
    "description": "Designed to introduce the student to major concepts and terminology in the field of human motor development. The content includes a description of how movement changes across the lifespan and the factors that influence and/or correlate with the changes. The Mountain of Motor Development model will help organize understanding of human motor development.",
